        <num>CC 3137</num>
        <heading>3137.  Personal or real security</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3137.  Personal or real security
Security is personal or real.
It is personal when it consists of an obligation undertaken to secure performance of
the obligation of another.
It is real when it consists of a right of preference established over property of the
obligor or of a third person to secure performance of an obligation.</p>
        </content>
